(- 2026-05-07: Kept public report generation sanitized and avoided raw systemctl status or full ) Tj
0 -12 Td
(process command-line capture.) Tj
0 -12 Td
(  Why: Full status and process listings can expose sensitive command-line arguments. Reports ) Tj
0 -12 Td
(use narrower systemd fields, sanitized journal excerpts, and explicit redaction before writing ) Tj
0 -12 Td
(TXT/PDF outputs.) Tj
0 -12 Td
(  Privacy note: Reports redact hostnames, usernames, IP addresses, keys, signatures, wallet-) Tj
0 -12 Td
(like hex strings, token-like values, and sensitive argument values.) Tj
0 -12 Td
(- 2026-05-10: Added a local OpenTelemetry Collector for the Monad metrics endpoint.) Tj
0 -12 Td
(  Why: Monad BFT requires a telemetry endpoint argument. The previous configuration pointed at ) Tj
0 -12 Td
(a local endpoint with no listener, causing repeated connection-refused errors. A localhost-only) Tj
0 -12 Td
( collector now provides the required endpoint without exporting private telemetry externally.) Tj
0 -12 Td
(  Privacy note: The report records only the operational change and reason. No raw telemetry ) Tj
0 -12 Td
(payloads, peer identities, public IP addresses, keys, command lines, or unlock values are ) Tj
0 -12 Td
(included.) Tj
0 -12 Td
() Tj
