0 -12 Td
(--------------) Tj
0 -12 Td
(- This report is generated from local system telemetry and Monad service logs on the mini PC.) Tj
0 -12 Td
(- Values are snapshots, not lab-grade benchmarks. Trends become more useful after multiple ) Tj
0 -12 Td
(four-hour samples.) Tj
0 -12 Td
(- The report intentionally avoids private identity material, validator keys, wallet-like ) Tj
0 -12 Td
(values, raw peer lists, public IPs, and command lines containing sensitive arguments.) Tj
0 -12 Td
(- Intended use: public community reporting about running a Monad node on smaller hardware while) Tj
0 -12 Td
( retaining useful operational data for technical readers.) Tj
